.IX Title "MarpaX::xPathLike 3"
.TH MarpaX::xPathLike 3 "2013-08-02" "perl v5.14.2" "User Contributed Perl Documentation"
.\" For nroff, turn off justification.  Always turn off hyphenation; it makes
